code>MessageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Um manipulador de eventos para o evento de carregamento do objeto <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>window</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">window.onload = <em>funcRef</em>;\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>funcRef é a função do manipulador a ser chamada quando o evento de carregamento do objeto </code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>window</code></a>&nbsp;<code>dispara.</code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">doSomethingElse</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>onload test<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Evento de carregamento detectado!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onload <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> load<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>O evento de carregamento dispara quando o documento acabou de ser carregado!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas","title":"Notas","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O evento de carregamento dispara&nbsp;no final do processo de carregamento do documento. Neste ponto, todos os objetos do documento estão no DOM, e todas as imagens, scripts, links e sub-frames terminaram de carregar.</p>\n\n<p>Existe também os&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Events\">Gecko-Specific DOM Events</a>, como o&nbsp;<code>DOMContentLoaded&nbsp;</code>e o&nbsp;<code>DOMFrameContentLoaded</code> (que pode ser manipulado utilizando o <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></a>) que são disparados após o DOM para a página ser construído, mas não espera outros recursos serem carregados.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#handler-onload\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'onload' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>DOMContentLoaded</code> event em&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Listening_to_events_in_Firefox_extensions#Simple_DOM_events\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Listening to events: Simple DOM events</a></li>\n <li>IIEF&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Immediately-invoked_function_expression\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external\">Immediately-invoked function expression</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Notas","id":"notas"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"Um manipulador de eventos para o evento de carregamento do objeto window.","popularity":0.0009,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onload","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onload/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers","title":"GlobalEventHandlers"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload","title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload"}],"pageTitle":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}